# Chadplotlib

## Basic usage

`pip install chadplotlib`

```python
import chadplotlib
chadplotlib.makeMeAChad()
```

Then just use matplotlib as you would.


## Packaging from source code

Building:

`python3 -m build`

Installing:

`pip install dist/*.whl`
